{"tid":2449892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：巴士公司若不加票價基層市民亦會受影響","createTime":"2021-03-17T04:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T07:59:31.000Z","uid":291865,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a6d907735cc85fc66044c8b84d3d4b9d98a10f","tid":2449892,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"林鄭：巴士公司若不加票價基層市民亦會受影響<br />\n<br />\n#港聞 四間巴士公司四月四日起將會加票價8.5%至12%，行政長官林鄭月娥指批准加價是困難的決定，但強調若不加價，最終基層市民也會受影響。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「有兩間是起碼七年及十年沒加過價。我們有大量數據可交給議員，我們已詳細看了他們的財務，每間巴士公司都『蝕到入肉』，如果不給他今次加價，結果是公營巴士服務將會大幅下降，而巴士公司要裁員或放無薪假，這些都是基層市民受到影響。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭：巴士公司若不加票價基層市民亦會受影響<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=427685&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427685%26refer%3DShare&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=f4394d30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427685%26refer%3DShare&h=3156eb64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=427685&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"2fa7228c15c62ac7c9e6767bf3d9c6b84f271d3d","tid":2449892,"uid":23707,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"爛閪黨鐵年年加咪又係年年壞"},{"pid":"4f213b4733f1e0ecfd54905c1c30fd193d4cf29b","tid":2449892,"uid":77196,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"做生意包賺？"},{"pid":"60864177c50c0b0735f34a08973f4b63116b6996","tid":2449892,"uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"限聚"},{"pid":"f9a169b9097bdb2f404759a0e77dfde7d862e919","tid":2449892,"uid":387466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"黨鐵加價基層市民無受到影響? dllm up mud 9"},{"pid":"6a47471e3c0e96d05988da38ef7876d17c963dec","tid":2449892,"uid":44841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sc